# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local secrets for the Cloudflare Pages Function (/api/insight — the AI Senior
# Analyst). Copy to `.dev.vars` (git-ignored) to test the AI layer locally with:
#
#     npx wrangler pages dev -- npm run dev
#   or, against a production build:
#     npm run build && npx wrangler pages dev dist
#
# A plain `npm run dev` (Vite only) does NOT run the function — the dashboard's
# instant Tier-1 readout still works everywhere; only the on-demand AI card needs
# this key. The browser NEVER receives it.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Your Anthropic API key (same one used by the insights generator).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional — override the model (defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6).
# INSIGHTS_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
